               <note>
                  <ab type="description">Gannat Tarrā is a hill in the northern part of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3577Gondar">Gondar</placeName> overlooking the city. It used to be
                     referred as Tǝgre Mač̣č̣ohyā (i.e. Cry of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6569Tegray">Tǝgrāy</placeName>), the area where people from
                     <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6569Tegray">Tǝgrāy</placeName> camped when they came to
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3577Gondar">Gondar</placeName> to appeal to the <roleName type="function">emperor</roleName>.</ab>
